{"tid":2464071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞馬遜傳封殺中国棉   來自「新疆」全下架","createTime":"2021-03-27T07:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T08:48:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":147,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"106a754e4266228c55689d1256830f7f5e41154c","tid":2464071,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:35:24.000Z","msg":"瑞典服裝品牌H&amp;M因公開聲明「拒用新疆棉」而遭到中國電商全面封殺，還有多項國際品牌也捲入新疆棉風暴，掀起中國網友高喊「拒買」抵制，還對許多代言相關品牌的藝人進行獵巫行動。如今就連美國電商平台亞馬遜（Amazon）也傳出封殺中國棉花，不僅下架許多中國棉商品，還要求中國出口商提供棉製品「不包含新疆棉花」的證明，再次掀起中國人怒火。<br />\n<br />\n根據《環球網》報導，中國豆瓣一名網友爆料，有通過亞馬遜向美國出口棉製品的中國商家透露，亞馬遜正在要求中國出口商提供「棉製品不包含新疆棉花」的證明。在一份疑似為亞馬遜發給中國出口商的文件中提到，美國政府規定禁止進口來自中國新疆的所有棉花製品，但中國有85%的棉花都來自新疆地區，目前有客人要求中國商家必須提供證明，否則來自中國的棉製品很可能被美國海關扣下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4RQgHn80_rynf2w_WRpCFw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTc0Ni4yMDY4OTY1NTE3MjQy/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/MBI6dKGtLKyUJmX7I9DX9Q--~B/aD01NDE7dz00NjQ7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/setn.com.tw/564d99ccfdabddd1d81e400d768d3ddc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F4RQgHn80_rynf2w_WRpCFw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTc0Ni4yMDY4OTY1NTE3MjQy%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FMBI6dKGtLKyUJmX7I9DX9Q--~B%2FaD01NDE7dz00NjQ7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F564d99ccfdabddd1d81e400d768d3ddc&h=9dac7a5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n爆料網友也提供了對話截圖，疑為中國商家的人表示，賣家根本無法提供這種保證出口產品不包含新疆棉花的證明，結果就是他們在亞馬遜上出售的棉製品被「一律下架」了。報導指出，雖然目前這則消息仍未得到亞馬遜官方證實，但根據先前的美媒報導，川普政府早在今年1月13日就以「強迫勞動」為由，全面封殺了來自中國新疆的棉花以及番茄等產品，因此爆料的情況看來並非空穴來風。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2I4IDA5uKFAMJCploTRrGg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTUyMy4wODg1MTIyNDEwNTQ2/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/.cUN.J2UtPbOLlnch2E2Cw--~B/aD00MzQ7dz01MzE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/setn.com.tw/8292419bb6e04dcc6bff225ef9f54673\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2I4IDA5uKFAMJCploTRrGg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTUyMy4wODg1MTIyNDEwNTQ2%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.cUN.J2UtPbOLlnch2E2Cw--~B%2FaD00MzQ7dz01MzE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F8292419bb6e04dcc6bff225ef9f54673&h=34977690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/亞馬遜傳封殺中國棉-來自新疆全下架-065532291.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E4%BA%9E%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%9C%E5%82%B3%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%A3%89-%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6-065532291.html&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr3%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=eece7962\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/亞馬遜傳封殺中國棉-來自新疆全下架-065532291.html</a>"},{"pid":"f5e0b531c0ce02a6fc49e9cd640c32debdf2e6da","tid":2464071,"uid":225798,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:36:27.000Z","msg":"死光最好"},{"pid":"71edd71147e81f1f483a172e7f93f469891bc15e","tid":2464071,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:36:35.000Z","msg":"等睇Amazon跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae619eb6cd79f1070e21ae194767ac039724208","tid":2464071,"uid":57677,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:37:35.000Z","msg":"原來紡織業係春袋"},{"pid":"0920297839f54909e87d88ade828eb46df2c25e7","tid":2464071,"uid":11148,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"支那人仲唔快啲抵制亞馬遜<br />\n<br />\n唔好再係亞馬遜賣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338e44d7eabcef0bac57bb5f9f324d5ea69e34e8","tid":2464071,"uid":102081,"like":2,